{"tid":691886,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歷史性時刻！沙特解禁首次向10女性頒發駕照","createTime":"2018-06-06T06:43:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T18:26:31.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cd94f4bec3ef74cbc24af640bf3fc6079d6ac291","tid":691886,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:43:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180606/_2018060613275761278_detail.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180606%2F_2018060613275761278_detail.jpg&h=cd68712b&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n1/1 沙特阿拉伯首次向10名女性批出駕照，6月24日起可以在沙特境內駕駛車輛。AP<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n沙特阿拉伯是全球唯一禁止女生駕駛汽車的國家，當地時間周一（4日），沙特阿拉伯交通總局向10名沙特女性發出駕駛執照，這是沙特歷史上首次向女性發出駕照，為三周後，即6月24日起可以在沙特境內駕駛車輛，無疑是沙國女性邁向自由的一大步。<br />\n<br />\n當天，共有10名沙特婦女來到位於首都利雅得的交通指揮部。當她們接過駕照時，興奮之情溢於言表。其中一名叫塔哈尼的婦女說：「這是一種難以形容的感覺，我無法形容這種感情。」 <br />\n<br />\n據沙特交通總局的聲明說，這10名女性已在國外獲得駕照。她們在沙特經過簡單的駕駛考試和視力檢查合格後已獲發駕照。<br />\n<br />\n長期以來，掌管社會和倫理的沙特宗教當局，以女性駕車可能引發性騷擾、陌生男女接觸等社會問題為由，反對女性駕車。雖然沙特法律沒有明文規定，但沙特交通部門從未給女性頒發過駕照。<br />\n<br />\n近年來，沙特王儲穆罕默德在其父薩勒曼國王支持下，對沙特社會、經濟和宗教進行大膽改革，出台了一系列舉措，賦予婦女更多權利。<br />\n<br />\n據沙特新聞部的一份聲明說，預計下周還將有2000名沙特女性會獲得駕照。根據交通部門計劃，沙特女性將從本月24日起，可以開車上路。<br />\n<br />\n此外，沙國也有5所大學為女性開辦駕駛課程，分別是努拉公主大學、阿卜杜勒阿齊茲國王大學、塔布克大學、塔伊夫大學、伊瑪目穆罕默德本沙特伊斯蘭大學。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/734113\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F734113&d=iSVeGoN7CwIAGDQczWzVl5nkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=16aebb5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F734113&h=8a97f773\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/734113</a>"},{"pid":"5cf6f1ab621c11c324220b179ca9bb25ac530089","tid":691886,"uid":120715,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:45:38.000Z","msg":"等睇一有交通意外，即刻全部沒收"},{"pid":"55c941dbc6c72a2f54b7b0eb6c591ae224a7c6e8","tid":691886,"uid":52459,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:45:49.000Z","msg":"女人渣車，真主保佑道路行人安全，阿門。"},{"pid":"0e11e78c6c3dae8f588310567457479768c045a5","tid":691886,"uid":65603,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:46:38.000Z","msg":"沙特有危險了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813b59a3479b963176b75bea1dfca04b0d60b554","tid":691886,"uid":164913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:46:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cbcce95f20f983c047f0fa39d508523e2df40b2e","tid":691886,"uid":46587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:50:08.000Z","msg":"連登仔少有同中東佬一齊支持嘅野<br />\n咁就玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7dd95d649e8f0ba7f9fa7fe10a1289764fe8dab","tid":691886,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:55:33.000Z","msg":"連登本土所撑其實只是毒撚報復 incel rebellion"},{"pid":"2d3c2c0362d4e9c3385fd1ceaacb7a1cc2407bd2","tid":691886,"uid":137627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T07:00:08.000Z","msg":"消滅人口政策<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660cc6dc9f6eddbad0282840b08cb16b66858067","tid":691886,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T07:02:17.000Z","msg":"RIP 沙特"},{"pid":"083d7f1aa5de407ef88121a96a1f8487eb7964fe","tid":691886,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:07:00.000Z","msg":"天堂有路你不走<br />\n地獄無門闖進來"},{"pid":"3e097c34f133ed67800106a463039766b4339ea3","tid":691886,"uid":137248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T08:13:36.000Z","msg":"慘喇連登仔唯一淨土無女人渣車既沙特都變埋左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgm